               wound proved mortal, and the other was therefore accused for the murther
            </rs>, but the Jury<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="16760117007"></xptr>perceiving by the evidence that he was compelled to draw to secure his life, brought in their verdict, <rs id="t16760117-3-verdict11" type="verdictDescription">
